Package: MERIDIAN
Title: Multi-Environment Research Integration: Data Intelligence and Agronomic Networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Salva", "Osuna", email = "salvadorosunacaballero@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application for comprehensive analysis of
    Multi-Environment Trial (MET) phenotypic data. Provides exploratory data
    analysis, ANOVA with variance components, stability analysis (AMMI, GGE,
    Eberhart-Russell, Wricke, Shukla), adaptation analysis with
    mega-environment identification, and automated report generation.
